{"tid":171730,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"王國興廉署舉報飯局賄選　曾俊華競選辦指無違規","createTime":"2017-03-25T13:21:40.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-25T13:21:40.000Z","uid":732,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"cc952a098aa6d6c18cf3f1af576cffa0bb8b21db","tid":171730,"uid":732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T13:21:40.000Z","msg":"【特首選舉】王國興廉署舉報飯局賄選　曾俊華競選辦指無違規：當晚出席者每人付500元<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/25/212121_9a9d6e40121e84049c130982b9d2ea90.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F25%2F212121_9a9d6e40121e84049c130982b9d2ea90.jpg&h=80d42674&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n由工聯會前立法會議員王國興成立的「23萬監察」，中午到廉政公署舉報行政長官候選人曾俊華，指他日前舉辦的「薯片私房菜」飯局，款待包括選委田北俊等人士，認為明顯涉及賄選。 <br />\n<br />\n曾俊華競選辦回覆《明報》查詢，稱當天出席嘉賓每人付款500元，作為晚膳食物及飲料費用，認為有關飯局無違規。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/25/212135_55813bac0951fe8b3030d5118e7091cd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F25%2F212135_55813bac0951fe8b3030d5118e7091cd.jpg&h=5c422e0e&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}